@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #333
skinparam RectangleBackgroundColor #F3F7FF
skinparam ArrowColor #444
title UC 01 - Autenticação Sistema (Comunicação)

rectangle "Usuario" as User
rectangle "AuthController" as C
rectangle "AuthService" as S
database "AuthDB" as DB
rectangle "ValidarPerfilService" as INC_ValidarPerfilService

left to right direction

User -down-> C : 1. Solicita "Autenticação Sistema"
C -down-> S : 2. Executa lógica
S --> INC_ValidarPerfilService : 3. Include ValidarPerfil
INC_ValidarPerfilService --> DB : 4. CRUD
DB --> INC_ValidarPerfilService : 5. Resultado
INC_ValidarPerfilService --> S : 6. Retorno
S --> DB : 7. CRUD principal
DB --> S : 8. Resultado
S --> C : 9. Resposta
C --> User : 10. Sucesso

note bottom of S
Includes: ValidarPerfil
end note

@enduml